                           Ormssonar</name>. Kålund tímasetti allt handritið til 17. aldar (<bibl>
                           <ref target="KKKat">Katalog</ref> (I) 1889: </bibl><ref
                           target="https://baekur.is/bok/c9ff2011-3cda-4197-90ef-7e14fc19f264/1/698"
                           >682</ref>).</p>
                     <p>Þegar Árni Magnússon fékk handritið voru <ref type="ms" target="#AM04-0630"
                           >AM 630 4to</ref> og <ref type="ms" target="AM04-0779-c-da">AM 779 c II
                           4to</ref> í sömu bók.</p>
                  </origin>

